## ðŸ›  Steps Taken (task 2)
1. Created a new Azure AD user using powershell - Isabel Garcia
. $passwordProfile = New-Object -TypeName Microsoft.Open.AzureAD.Model.PasswordProfile
. $passwordProfile.Password = "Pa55w.rd1234"
. Connect-AzureAD
. $domainName = ((Get-AzureAdTenantDetail).VerifiedDomains)[0].Name
. New-AzureADUser -DisplayName 'Isabel Garcia' -PasswordProfile $passwordProfile -UserPrincipalName "Isabel@$domainName" -AccountEnabled $true -MailNickName 'Isabel'
2. Created a new Azure AD group using powershell - JuniorAdmins
. New-AzureADGroup -DisplayName 'JuniorAdmins' -MailEnabled $false -SecurityEnabled $true -MailNickName JuniorAdmins
. Get-AzureADGroup
3. Added user (Isabel Garcia) to Group (JuniorAdmins)
. Add-AzADGroupMember -MemberUserPrincipalName Isabel@44356.onmicrosoft.com -TargetGroupDisplayName JuniorAdmins
. Get-AzADGroupMember -GroupDisplayName JuniorAdmins

